            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>
               <expan><abbr>Θ</abbr><ex>εοῖς</ex></expan>
               <expan><abbr>Κ</abbr><ex>αταχθονίοις</ex></expan>.
                    <lb n="2"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Kallityche">Καλλιτύχη</name>
               </persName> ἐνθά
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>δε κεῖται, ἥτις
                    <lb n="4"/>ἔζησεν ἔτη <num value="14">
                  <hi rend="supraline">ιδ</hi>ʹ</num>,
                    <lb n="5"/>καὶ <persName>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Gelasis">Γελάσις</name>
               </persName> ζή
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/>σας ἔτη <num value="3">
                  <hi rend="supraline">γ</hi>ʹ</num>, <expan><abbr>μ</abbr><ex>ηνας</ex></expan>
               <num value="5">
                  <hi rend="supraline">ε</hi>ʹ</num>.
                    <lb n="7"/>
               <persName>
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Aurelia">
                     <del rend="erasure">A</del>
                     <expan><abbr><hi rend="small">Α</hi>ὐρηλ</abbr><ex>ία</ex></expan>
                  </name>
                  <name type="gentilicium" key="Vibia">
                     <expan><abbr>Οὐιβ</abbr><ex>ία</ex></expan>
                  </name>
                  <name type="cognomen" key="Sabina">Σαβεῖ
                    <lb n="8" break="no"/>να</name>
               </persName>, <expan><abbr>θρεπτ</abbr><ex>οῖς</ex></expan> ἀξίοις
                    <lb n="9"/>
               <expan><abbr>μ</abbr><ex>νήμης</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>χ</abbr><ex>αρίν</ex></expan>.
                </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the gods of the underworld. Kallityche lies here, who lived for 14 years,
                    and Gelasis, having lived for 3 years (and) 5 months. Aurelia Vibia Sabina (made
                    this) for (her) worthy homeborn slaves, for their memory.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary"><!-- notes go here -->
            <p>θρέπτοι (line 8) were either homeborn slaves (vernae) or foster children (alumni).</p>
         </div>
